{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269080/extras/21Untitled.jpg?t=1668171640\" /><br><br>ALIVE is an escape room indie game, focused on the story of Chris and professor William Johnson. Chris is a young man, in his 20\u2019s. He has no money and no one by his side. He is all alone. He lives in a pretty small apartment. He works in a job he hates, with a very small paycheck. Chris tries out a game he saw in his popup ads in order to cover his debt, so he won\u2019t get kicked out of his apartment.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269080/extras/FinishLevel1_Wide.gif?t=1668171640\" /><br>Professor William Johnson is a former psychologist who suffers from trauma. Now he is obsessed with showing the dark side of humanity's sin of greed. William then creates the game named &quot;ALIVE&quot; and offers a grand prize for the winner.\u200b<br><br>Learn about humanity\u2019s sin of greed in an escape room game where you play as Chris, a poor young man who looks for easy ways to get money but ends up in a virtual reality he can\u2019t escape. <br><br>Help Chris escape the rooms while uncovering the story behind them, and the man who created them.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1269080/extras/Level2Flashlight_Wide.gif?t=1668171640\" /><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Open Door Games</h2></strong><br>Open Door Games is an indie game studio that focuses on creating games that make you want to play mostly because of the story.<br>We are two childhood friends that each have grown on a different path in his life. As one went to programming and game development, the other went for a cinematic path. Thanks to our long-term friendship over the years we have managed to find a way to dissolve our paths into the project that now we can gladly call, Open Door Games.<br><br